GUI Test Checklist

Beat Editor Tab:
    • Parameters (genre, theme, instrument, key, tempo) work
    • Generate Beat creates chords, melody, drums
    • Regenerate Chords updates only chords
    • Regenerate Melody updates only melody
    • Kick/Snare/Hi‑hat/Open Hat buttons update only that drum
    • Save Project saves a .beatproj file
    • Load Project restores the saved state

Full Track Tab:
    • Parameters (genre, theme, instrument, key, tempo) work
    • TTS provider selection (placeholder vs elevenlabs)
    • Generate Full Track creates beat, lyrics, voice, and mixed WAV
    • Regenerate Beat updates beat, voice, and mixed track
    • Regenerate Lyrics updates lyrics, voice, and mixed track
    • Regenerate Voice updates voice and mixed track
    • Regenerate Chords updates chords, voice, and mixed track
    • Regenerate Melody updates melody, voice, and mixed track
    • Regenerate Drums updates drums, voice, and mixed track
    • Save Project saves a .trackproj file
    • Load Project restores the saved state

General:
    • No crashes during normal use
    • Error messages appear when expected (e.g., missing API key)